      "content": "okay i get it, but i really dont have time for an appointment this week. my tremors are getting a little worse and now i'm feeling a bit dizzy too. if i just wait a couple days to see if it goes away on its own, is there any specific thing i should watch for that would actually make it an emergency? like i just want to know if i can safely wait until the weekend.",
